Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:39.58,EngED,,0,0,0,,I gaze upon the never-ending world's destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:46.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
